{"title":"[eCommerce] Markdown (copy)","type":"markdown","aggs":[],"params":{"fontSize":12,"openLinksInNewTab":false,"markdown":"### Sample Multiple Data Source Connections Dashboard

This dashboard contains sample data from multiple data sources. You can view it, search it, and interact with the visualizations from different data sources.

| Visualization prefix | Data Source                                                                                                                                               | Notes            |
|----------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------|
| [US Region]          | [US OpenSearch Cluster](https://playground.opensearch.org/app/management/opensearch-dashboards/dataSources) | External cluster |
| [EU Region]          | [EU OpenSearch Cluster](https://playground.opensearch.org/app/management/opensearch-dashboards/dataSources) | External cluster |
| [JP Region]          | JP OpenSearch Cluster                                                                                                                                     | Local/Default cluster  |

For more information on setting up and exploring this feature, see the OpenSearch [launch blog](https://opensearch.org/blog/community/2022/11/multiple-data-source/) and [documentation](https://opensearch.org/docs/latest/dashboards/discover/multi-data-sources/). You can try out this feature in your local environment or the [OpenSearch playground](https://playground.opensearch.org/app/home#/). To leave feedback, visit the [OpenSearch Forum](https://forum.opensearch.org/t/feedback-experimental-feature-connect-to-external-data-sources/11144). If you're interested in contributing to this experimental feature, consider contributing to the OpenSearch Dashboards [repository](https://github.com/opensearch-project/OpenSearch-Dashboards).
"}}
